    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepts the simulation evidence package for regulatory submission. All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated; seven are formally assessed and six are identified as epistemic gaps. The package is accepted on the basis that the achieved credibility levels, while below required levels for MRL 5, are consistent with the state of the art for CFD hemolysis prediction and the residual gaps are acknowledged in the submission narrative.",
